caption.p: Virions in the ultra sections of infected Vero E6 cells under electron microscope. (A, F) uninfected cells, (B, G) mock-treated SARS-CoV-2 virus infected cells, (C, D, H, I) infected cells with LH treatment, (E, J) infected cells with remdesivir treatment. White arrows indicated the spindle sharp of viral particles in infected cells with LH treatment.
